{"tid":324044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[DQ 4] 促林鄭酌情不同期補選　 朱凱廸稱泛民會釋出善意","createTime":"2017-07-16T06:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T09:00:26.000Z","uid":49388,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"369a3b44891e38d2998d6c1aaa7ea42fdd2cf1c0","tid":324044,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:39:46.000Z","msg":"4名立法會議員在7月14日被高院裁定宣誓無效，喪失議員資格。有泛民議員今日（7月16日）表示，行政長官林鄭月娥有酌情權，如果她決定不同期補選，民主派一定會釋出善意。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員朱凱廸今日（7月16日）在香港電台節目《城市論壇》中表示，特首林鄭月娥要負責解開政治上的結，她可以運用手上很多的酌情權。朱凱廸又指，若果她承諾不乘人之危，補選不會同期執行，將早前先後6名喪失議員資格的議席一併重選，「畀建制派攞多兩席」；或者選擇不收訟費，「若果佢（林鄭月娥）有咁嘅表現嘅話，其實民主派都一定會釋出善意。」<br />\n7月14日，泛民議晚上在政府總部公民廣場外舉行集會，指會抗爭到底。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-16-2017/40490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-16-2017%2F40490&d=n5LJYnjb56BN7rXI7crcNJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=91f3abfd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-16-2017/40490</a>"},{"pid":"b3002c1a1db87e7c4a3dffc6ddb4fada2cc5296e","tid":324044,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abb47f3163b2152d4855e41c13bb7946246d72d","tid":324044,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"釋出善意"},{"pid":"9f98174ca104357a91a60159391471c57473cc5d","tid":324044,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>釋出善意</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484daff07d8b8d079e6be76a29fcd648a8398a2b","tid":324044,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9f109c72acd4ed