<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170714/large/1500036785_71a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170714%2Flarge%2F1500036785_71a6.png&h=77328a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼青年新政梁頌恆及游蕙禎被政府褫奪立法會議員資格後，法庭再裁定政府司法覆核勝訴，認為羅冠聰、劉小麗、梁國雄及姚松炎的宣誓不合規格，宣佈由去年10月12日宣誓當日起計，4人議席失效，若上訴失敗，便有6席要補選。科大社會學部副教授成名預計，建制派在九西及新東應最少奪2席，地區直選議席將增至18席，相反非建制派會減至17席，喪失在分組點票時的否決權。<br />\n<br />\n他分析，在九西及新東的兩大選區，建制派必然會派人參選，即使泛民派代表出戰補選，在比例代表制下，估計建制派會在九西及新東取得最少2席。而只有1席出缺的港島區，將按單議席單票制補選，估計對非建制派有利。<br />\n<br />\n至於非建制派能否有策略可全奪回6席，他稱，「我覺得係悲觀」，因在比例代表制下，建制派有一定核心的支持者，即鐵票，認為非建制派「無可能6席贏返晒返來」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56957050&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56957050%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170714&d=n5LJYnjb56BN7rXI7crcNJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=696fc2c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56957050%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170714&h=5dd843a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56957050&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170714</a><br />\n新東無可能分開補選<br />\n再加埋極可能被DQ新西2個<br />\n泛民必失2席"},{"pid":"cd99fabd382ec39c2dbdb14b0bb9e0deea8d32f8","tid":324044,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成幾個月時間<br />\n大把野可以做晒<br />\n修改議事規則<br />\n一地兩檢。。。</blockquote><br />\n好似立法會都有暑假放 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n準備補選最快要用4至6月時間</blockquote><br />\n而且一定要等埋終審法院判決"},{"pid":"d9bf4c3f4573fd721c6235177cee876c61063b98","tid":324044,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"963bfcafc669a2e7413e4e394f6860b3411426cb","tid":324044,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n新東無可能分開補選<br />\n再加埋極可能被DQ新西2個<br />\n泛民必失2席</blockquote><br />\n1定攞唔足冇咗既位<br />\n直選過半優勢都重奪唔到<br />\n係睇最後dq幾多個,建制拎唔拎到3分2=47席"},{"pid":"7388fd85b6ffbbf4f3cb09c5e36d0e50872e9f7e","tid":324044,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俾人恰到上心口 善你老母咩戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港法治制度俾人輪姦完，還要向強姦犯跪地求饒釋出善意?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求你再女女女多次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57263f1230071e8d3dd5f912b143711bac69d5c","tid":324044,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俾人恰到上心口 善你老母咩戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港法治制度俾人輪姦完，還要向強姦犯跪地求饒釋出善意?</blockquote><br />\n叫佢哋姦還姦 唔好整爛個BRA"},{"pid":"b5096af9c4aed8646e2f512173731574f5f8eb90","tid":324044,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如叫7嬸解散立法會重選好過</blockquote><br />\n50條?</blockquote><br />\n本身cy舖好哂條路<br />\n連任到既話依個時間佢就無敵<br />\n結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱先話要改善關係d dq就係咁出爐"},{"pid":"52dea3baa7d1bad4f8ec0ae231d7cfc103118393","tid":324044,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4207f4e5ddd4060f570c31f6b6ee51daf4c7456e","tid":324044,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"當權者都wfc你d 善意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}